    <h1>Espressioni algebriche</h1>
    <p>Risolvi la seguente disequazione.</p>
    <p id="display"></p>
    <p>Puoi controllare la <a href="#" onclick="show_answer();">risposta</a>. Per vedere un altro esercizio sullo stesso argomento basta ricaricare la pagina.</p>
    <p id="answer"></p>
    
    <script>
      pieces = [
        ["5(3-4x) + 14x - \\frac{11}{6} \\lt -10x - \\frac{10}{3}\\left(\\frac{8x-15}{20}\\right)", "x \\lt -2"],
        ["(x-1)(x+1) - (x-3)^2 \\lt 3", "x \\lt \\frac{13}{6}"],
        ["(x-1)^2 - 3x \\lt (x-3)(x+3)", "x \\gt 2"],
        ["4(5x - 1) + 2(3x + 1)^2 \\gt 3x(6x+5) - 2x - 3", "x \\gt - \\frac{1}{19}"],
        ["(2x - 1)^2 - 3(2+x) \\leq (2x + 3)(2x-3) + 2(x+3)", "x \\geq -\\frac{2}{9}"],
        ["(3x - 1)(3x + 1) - \\left(1 - \\frac{1}{2}x\\right)^2 + \\frac{1}{4}(x+1)^2 - 9x^2 \\lt 0", "x \\lt \\frac{7}{6}"],
        ["x^2(2-x) + (x-2)^3 \\leq -5(1-2x) + (2x + 1)(1-2x)", "x \\leq 2"],
        ["\\left(\\frac{1}{2} - x\\right)^2 - (x+1)^2 \\lt -\\left[1 - \\left( \\frac{2x + 1}{6}\\right) \\right] + \\frac{1+2x}{3}", "x \\gt - \\frac{1}{16}"],
        ["\\left( \\frac{1}{3} - \\frac{5}{3}x\\right)^2 \\lt \\frac{5}{9}x(x-2) + \\left(x - \\frac{4}{9}x\\right)4x", "\\mbox{impossibile}"],
        ["\\frac{(x-1)(x+1)}{2} + \\left[ \\frac{x-5}{4} - \\left( \\frac{1}{2}x + 1 \\right)\\right] -\\frac{(x-3)^2}{2} \\gt 0", "x \\gt \\frac{29}{11}"],
        ]
      chosen = pieces[Math.floor((Math.random() * pieces.length))];
      $("#answer").hide();
      $("#display").append("\\[ " + chosen[0] + " \\]");
      
      function show_answer() {
        $("#answer").show();
        }
    </script>
   
    
